All Classes and Interfaces

クラス
クラス
説明
Cell
Representation of a Towny plot, based on it's Coord, used for manipulation in FlagWar.
CellAttackCanceledEvent
Event fired when an attack on a Cell is being cancelled.
CellAttackEvent
Event fired when a Towny Cell is being attacked.
CellAttackThread
Each CellUnderAttack's attack thread, extending the TimerTask.
CellDefendedEvent
Event fired when a Towny Cell was defended by the defending team.
CellUnderAttack
Extension of a Cell when under attack.
CellWonEvent
Event fired when a Cell attack has been successful.
ConfigLoader
Handles loading of configuration files.
FlagWar
The main class of the TownyAdvanced: FlagWar addon.
FlagWarAPI
FlagWar Public API.
FlagWarBlockListener
Listens for interactions with Blocks, then runs a check if qualified.
FlagWarConfig
Transitional class holding values from the configuration file, as well as defining some defaults.
FlagWarCustomListener
General-purpose event listener for tracking Towny and FlagWar events.
FlagWarEntityListener
Entity Listener.
HologramUpdateThread
Each CellUnderAttack's hologram timer thread, extending the TimerTask.
LocaleUtil
Utility class for handling the loading of translation property files.
Messaging
Handles messaging for FlagWar.
OutlawListener
Listener class for Outlaw-related events and balancing.
Translate
Helper class for abstracting away locale utilities.
WarzoneListener
WarZone Listener, ported from Towny.
